**AI-Powered Detection of VAT Fraud Using Machine Learning**

## ðŸ” Summary  
This project applies machine learning classification models to flag suspicious VAT filings using historical audit and revenue data. It was **deployed at the Kenya Revenue Authority (KRA)** and flagged over **$12M in fraudulent tax activity**.

